'''''bôr''''' (plural '''''bŷr''''') is a noun meaning "steadfast, trustworthy, a faithful vassal" in [[Sindarin]]. Compare with ''[[vor]]'' in [[Quenya]].

Examples:
* [[Borlach]] = "Faithful Flame"
* [[Boromir]] = "Faithful Jewel"

